            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[<h2>What's New in 3.6.3</h2><ul></ul><p><strong>Improved</strong></p><ul><li>More reliable AI Rename when cloud requests time out</li><li>More dependable folder monitoring during large file changes</li><li>Zush now asks App Store users for a rating after successful Pro rename sessions</li></ul><p><strong>Fixed</strong></p><ul><li>Fixed startup setup after completing onboarding</li><li>Fixed update prompts in the direct-download version</li><li>Reduced unnecessary macOS keychain prompts</li></ul>
]]></description>
